name: Tun TuN
text: For all truckers coming here pick up times are strick only get here 30 min before time or u will have to wait . Overall super fast loading but be carefull they load me over weight even at 42 ft . Office lady is nice but a novice when it comes to trucking industry , I let her know i have equipment on the truck that tells me am over weight in last axel and still she refused to fix the load instead send me 14 miles Each way on a bunch of street lights to a LOVE’S to weight the truck . To much waste Off time loss almost 3 hours in all of this BS .  Waste of Time and Money.
